        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_airhostess_03",
        "zh_CN": "您乘坐的目的地为新恒提罗的航班A4359,将于半小时后降落，请您……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "耳边传来航班的广播播报，米娅看了眼终端上的时间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "自己已经离开熙澜海，离开那个人快两个小时了……",
        "disable": 0
