    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可为什么脸还是那么烫呢……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恰巧空乘路过，米娅连忙招了招手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_npc098_01",
        "zh_CN": "能麻烦给我一杯冰吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "空乘人员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_airhostess_01",
        "zh_CN": "诶？是加冰的饮料吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_npc098_02",
        "zh_CN": "不不不，一杯冰块就好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "空乘人员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_airhostess_02",
        "zh_CN": "好的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "空乘人员刚递过杯子，米娅就迫不及待地将其贴在了脸颊上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_npc098_03",
        "zh_CN": "啊……我到底是怎么想的，居然说了这么丢脸的话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想到早晨发生的一切，米娅脸上的温度不仅没有退却，还反而更火热了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为了分散注意力，米娅从随身的包里摸出纸笔，随意地涂涂画画起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "杂乱无序的线条像是有自己的想法，在无形间重组，最后竟是勾勒出一张戴墨镜的面容。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "凝视了好一会，米娅又鬼使神差地细化起背景。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "阳光，椰子树，偶然飞过的海鸟……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "纸上的人和景色渐渐鲜活起来，离别的时刻又在米娅脑中重新上演起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女拖着行李箱，匆匆忙忙向停机坪跑去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "按照今天的安排，她会先乘世界树的私人飞机到菲洛索亚，再从菲洛索亚转机回新恒提罗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "每个环节留下的时间容错都很少，但偏偏自己昨天又在水上乐园玩得太过尽兴。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "米娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_npc098_04",
        "zh_CN": "我错了，我再也不熬夜了，拜托拜托，一定要赶上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然还在清晨，凉爽的风不断呼呼而过，但米娅还是感到额头出了一层薄汗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "等好不容易赶到后，少女已经是上气不接下气，一边扶着行李箱，一边用手给自己扇风。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "要早知道你来的这么晚，我就顺带叫你起床了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_npc098_05",
        "zh_CN": "唔？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一看到我，米娅脸上瞬间绽放出热情的笑容。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_npc098_06",
        "zh_CN": "要是早知道分析员想送我上机……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_npc098_07",
        "zh_CN": "我昨晚就该和大家一起住在你的房间，等你叫我起床了~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32st3_npc098_08",
        "zh_CN": "所以……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米娅向我走近几步，两人之间的距离缩短到几乎能感受到彼此呼吸的程度。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而她此时热烈而直接的眼神，倒映在了我的眸中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
